/* WIRING DIAGRAM:
 *  
 *  ARDUINO     RTC     LCD DISPLAY
 *  -------------------------------
 *      A4      SDA         SDA
 *      A5      SCL         SCL
 *      5V      VCC         VCC
 *     GND      GND         GNG 
